Name: My Soldiers
About the game: LET THE STORY BEGIN My Soldiers places you in the role of a soldier who's new to a post near the border, you are gonna meet three soldiers here. So 'My Soldiers' tells a story that happens in this small post with these guys. These guys have different personalities, There are 3 routes and over 100 CGs in all. Contains mature content, 18 and older only. FEATURES 5 Full Long-form Routes 3 Main Characters 1 Secret Route Over 200 full scene illustrations 36 Animated Hot Scenes Hours of playing time, and steamy stories that are decided by your choices Windows, Android Available
